></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">8.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家在明知或应知商品需要经过京东的入仓查验程序的情况下，故意采取各种手段或策略来规避、逃避或躲避这个程序的行为。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">8.2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">8.2.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">商家所售卖的商品未经过京东认可的机构在鉴定仓的鉴定/鉴别：</span></strong></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: none; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规情节</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: lef