: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规商品下架</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">超额资金冻结止付</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">扣除违约金：币种（人民币）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">情节严重</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">第四次或第五次违规</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规商品下架</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">超额资金冻结止付</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">扣除违约金：币种（人民币）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10000~20000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">情节极其严重</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">累计五次及以上</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规商品下架</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">超额资金冻结止付</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">店铺-延迟结算28天</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">禁止报名营销活动28天</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">扣除违约金：币种（人民币）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0.75pt;\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">50000~100000</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 75pt; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0.75pt;\" colspan=\"4\" width=\"100\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：年度不清零，累计处理。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">除上述处理措施外，京东有权对商家采取限制渠道专属服务费、限制商家下单和支付权益、终止合作、交易限额、冻结其在京东的款项、延迟结算、下架违规商品、禁售商品、取消相关标识及追回相关款项、关闭账户功能等处理措施。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三章附则</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京东开放平台商家的行为，发生在本规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京东有权视违规店铺的违规严重程度，依据法律法规、协议、《京东开放平台关联店铺管理规则》等，对违规店铺的关联店铺立即做出处理。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">13</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京东有权结合实际情形及违规程度，对商家采取必要的临时市场管控，处理手段包括但不限于：全店商品下架、店铺清退、冻结钱包、延迟结算等。此外，京东有权对商家违规行为导致的媒体曝光、行政监管、消费者投诉等进行处理，并要求商家承担违约责任。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">14</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京东依据法律法规、规则等对商家采取处理措施及追究违约责任，不影响京东依据协议约定等追究商家的违约责任。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">15</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、本规则于2025年7月7日公示，于2025年7月14日生效。</span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</div>",
